   computer aided student drawings. Such model would assist in full
   automating the educators task or serving as a decision support system.
   Given the shared fundamental skills at least for fundamental drawing
   skills, the model has the potential to be used as Cloud service to be
   utilized by various distributed users. This would only serve to support
   and improve the model's performance given the additional training it
   could provide.
