   Soc; Asian Pacific Neural Network Soc; Polish Neural Network Soc;
   Russian Neural Network Soc},
Abstract = {A new method to design learning laws for neural networks with continuous
   dynamics is proposed in this study. The learning method is based on the
   so-called double-averaged descendant technique (DAS-GDT), which is a
   variant of the gradient-descendant method. The learning law implements a
   double averaged algorithm which filters the effect of uncertainties of
   the states, which are continuously measurable. The learning law
   overcomes the classical assumption on the strict convexity of the
   functional with respect to the weights. The photocatalytic ozonation
   process of a single contaminant is estimated using the learning law
   design proposed in this study.},
